CuriositàNel films of Roberto Rossellini, A pilot returns, 1942), the protagonist, Ten. Pilot Rossati, enters service in 161ª Squadron Bombardment of the Terrestrial, however non-existent but fitted quite so with the CANT Z. 1007.One of the most important works of Gabriele D'annunzio, the third of the "Praises of the sky, sea, earth and heroes", has the title as the code name of the plane that is precisely Alcyone.
